Additional Note:
The metric reported for each individual class in the paper is the F1 score.
————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————

This is an anonymous code repository.

The LLM-based data augmentation proposed in our work is stored in the folder LLM_data. Specifically, 
the audio augmentation information is contained in dev_prosody_llm_all.jsonl, train_prosody_llm_all.jsonl, 
and test_prosody_llm_all.jsonl. In our experiments, we use the augmented feature "one_liner".

For the text and vision modalities, the augmented information is stored in Train_Dia_labeled_semantic_masked, Test_Dia_labeled_semantic_masked, 
and dev_Dia_labeled_semantic_masked. 
For the text modality,the augmented features correspond to the column semantic_explanation, 
and the emotion-word-masked features are stored in semantic_explanation__masked. For the vision modality, 
the augmented features are stored in the column vision_caption.

Environment Information

Python: 3.12 (Ubuntu 22.04)

PyTorch: 2.8.0 + cu128

NumPy: 2.3.2

CUDA: 12.8

GPU: RTX PRO 6000 × 1 (96 GB)

CPU: 22 vCPU Intel Xeon Platinum 8470Q

Memory: 110 GB

⚠️ Note: If the environment changes (e.g., PyTorch version, CUDA, GPU number/model, or Python version),
results may vary slightly even when using the same random seed. This is due to floating-point differences and GPU parallel computation.

The downloaded MELD dataset contains a small number of potentially erroneous samples, where the text does not match the corresponding video 
or the video duration is abnormally long. For these cases, we treat the text modality as the reference and mark the other two modalities as missing. 
In addition, due to occasional instability in online token transmission during AI-based data augmentation,
a small number of augmented samples may be missing. The proposed model is designed to be robust to such partial modality absence.

If you are able to access Baidu Cloud, our PKL dataset is available at this link for use. 

File shared via Baidu Cloud: Pkl_Data
Link: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1Q3__2FnHdt8jSjhcYKzK0g

Extraction code: h9i7
